Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:36.00,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be1\an8}翻译：味精；特效：Noeru、Tiger Soldier；\N后期：zipwinmax；繁化：黑羽侖人。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}さらば　昨日までの口づけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}さらば　いとおしき胸の痛みよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まあ　それはそれとしてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何とか今日も生きています
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}孤独とか過去とか噂とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:30.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}欲望とか身内とかクセとか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明日からおれらきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.62,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう笑われずにすみそうだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}“信じていればいつか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}気持ちはちゃんと伝わってくよ…”と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ふざけないでよ　だって　そうじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう　どこへも逃げたりしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}誰が“yes！”といって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だって　昨日の場所には戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君といた場所には
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もう　誰にも言い訳したくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.01,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だから“yes！”といって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.03,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}だって誰でもいーわけない　そうじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君じゃなきゃ意味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}こたえなんか　誰も知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.00,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}再见了  终结于昨日的亲吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.35,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}再见了  我那可怜的心伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}算了  不提也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:20.11,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天也先想方设法活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.79,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}什么孤独  过去  和传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:30.88,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}什么欲望  全身  跟癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.15,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}从明天起  我一定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.62,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不用再强颜欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.53,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}“只要坚信这一点  总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.51,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会将心情完全传达…”这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.33,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}别逗了啦  难道不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.61,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我也已经不想再逃到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:59.48,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虽然有人说“yes！”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.49,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}可还是无法回到昨日的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.71,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那是和你一起度过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:11.68,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}已经不想向任何人辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:16.01,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}所以说“yes！”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.03,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}因为任何人都已不再辩解  不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.47,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不是你的话就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:29.59,opzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}答案什么的  谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日同学  今天还去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  侑子小姐老是乱使唤人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说啥晚饭的菜每天都要换花样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不事先预备好  根本没可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼你懂不懂怎么过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是四月一日同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能做出很好吃的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  如果是给小葵做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没戏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说土豆炖肉是在炖牛肉的基础上发明出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.65,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,410)}报  恩{\fs16}\N\N{\fs18}回 馈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日式西式中式都一个一个做过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  在这种天气里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是得吃那个～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  就是这个味道～诱人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手  手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到你了真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东煮店老板的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么除了手以外都看不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量还很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法全身都进到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你送我气球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转交给关东煮店老板的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说是百鬼夜行时蒙他搭救的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那个…我做了关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是气球的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那个就是给你的回礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东煮～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东煮～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸的关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂你们两个  在火边上玩很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日  四月一日  粗心大意～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个气球本身就是回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可结果又得到了那个的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那样  小狐狸就高兴得不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日也来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是给你的回礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年糕和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油豆腐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二重唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮啊  浮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来的半片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会沉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你付出对等的代价  我就能帮你实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得我那么紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是要我跟包吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我搬的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该和这个没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我们家那个不太好用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这个真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西鬼才搬得回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得买这个才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不是挺小的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说那个  那个可不会制冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是俗话说的「哑炮」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事很常有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都是量产品  没有什么特别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可一买回家就是坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么  马上就会出故障
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还很容易买到那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这种事怎么可能靠看的就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的  你还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目不转睛地看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现什么和其他不一样的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  是哑炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想买那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前的四月一日就会买了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那半只右眼的效力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是提高了视力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是买这个冰箱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大个的  没可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我要自己搬回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来为您打包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了没可能啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都说过没可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的促销商品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚  刚才说话的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是老夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个样子会有那种声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该吐槽的地方是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有奇怪的东西冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个该遭天谴的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在闹什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个遭天谴的小鬼是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是我店里的打工仔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那个传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你能不能好好调教一下佣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…站在人身上说人家坏话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼  居然拿老夫当怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是够奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫是掌管雷电的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人称老夫为「雷兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在书上看过雷兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样更威严一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也不会搞得像家电城里的促销商品…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不长教训
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼  把老夫从这里弄出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么要我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再被电可怎么受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能空手去摸雷兽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  多亏有你  这样就不用买新的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是报答你救我出来的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你出来的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  四月一日  痛吗  是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修得时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  为什么你会跑到电器城去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有个地方想去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有从天上下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果一下来就被那建筑物给吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被电磁波给吸引过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  于是就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你想去的地方是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚应该是个赏月的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我能和你一起前往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是和你一道的话就不会走错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  四月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小葵也叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵也一起来～小葵小葵～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  要去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是要去实现四月一日的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道小葵肯定乐意来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我实现愿望是很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么又把这家伙给叫来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又是这种桥段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里都不紧不慢地出现的闲人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百目鬼同学也在的话  那东西更容易出现了嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有可能会那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  管狐也这么想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多的话才好玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  实际上我也是那么想的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊  奇怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸的关东煮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  光是闻的就要流口水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  牛板筋一串
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  又换新铺子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福  只是翻新了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  喜欢关东煮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的关东煮  很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅子还你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来还锅子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说也有这个原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的关东煮的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是怎么可以给回礼的回礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  猫娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的时候要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  侑子大姐  上次多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都先到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也和大家就个伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板  再烫壶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  一起来的小姐要点什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼不要去那边  上老夫这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是也来帮忙做呢～说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一起来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先弄个萝卜  然后做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是蒟蒻加牛蒡卷加土豆加粉条…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一给你镜头你就点菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你的胃还是青春期的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时下不景气  就连收到的梦也净是噩梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝卜  鸡蛋还有年糕包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带酒来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！这可是十二年窖藏的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨童女  座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们也被关东煮的味道吸引来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很难找到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这里人还真是不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是下次再来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  打扰一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是顺利地看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说起来店老板做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到碗关东煮就哭了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你又把她弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄哭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这种桥段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侑子大姐还是那么心疼那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最后还是完成了百鬼夜行  拿到了甘露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他那买来的梦  已经培育成了很棒的梦了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也是来庆祝这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他可是笨到敢空手来摸我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小葵的份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入味萝卜还有彩色的年糕包  然后是厚油豆…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐  你也喜欢油豆腐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  就这么点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁豆腐和鱼子团
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去盛  自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是鱼糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～下起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是场阵雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨童女～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个稍等一下再弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  老夫也该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这就要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫已经吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是香茶和关东煮的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像烟火一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜～  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了～今晚要喝个够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨童女  拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  来吃个够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝个够吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月一日  拜托加把劲吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是杀人啊！
